(string) (len=3042) "IDENT\tprogram\nIDENT\tAnimatedPendulum\nCOMMENT\t**********************************************\nCOMMENT\t*       Program:    Simple_Pendulum_Solver   *\nCOMMENT\t*       Written_By: Brian Downing            *\nCOMMENT\t*                   Fordham University       *\nCOMMENT\t*       Date:       October 23rd, 1990       *\nCOMMENT\t**********************************************\nIDENT\tImplicit\nIDENT\tNone\nCOMMENT\t*\nCOMMENT\t*       Declare double precision variables.\nCOMMENT\t*\nIDENT\tdouble\nIDENT\tprecision\nIDENT\ta\n,\t,\nIDENT\tg\n,\t,\nIDENT\tl\n,\t,\nIDENT\tt\n,\t,\nIDENT\tdt\n,\t,\nIDENT\tw\n,\t,\nIDENT\tPi\n,\t,\nIDENT\tTheta\n,\t,\nIDENT\tThetaM\nCOMMENT\t*\nCOMMENT\t*       Initialize some constant values.\nCOMMENT\t*\nIDENT\tPi\n=\t=\nIDENT\t4\n.\t.\nIDENT\t0\n*\t*A\nIDENT\tTAN\n(\t(\nIDENT\t1\n.\t.\nIDENT\t0\n)\t)\nCOMMENT\t*\nCOMMENT\t*       Clear screen and then prompt for real numbers for variables.\nCOMMENT\t*\nIDENT\tCall\nIDENT\tCLS\nIDENT\twrite\n(\t(\nIDENT\t5\n,\t,\nIDENT\t100\n)\t)\nIDENT\tread\n*\t*,\nIDENT\tdt\nIDENT\twrite\n(\t(\nIDENT\t5\n,\t,\nIDENT\t200\n)\t)\nIDENT\tread\n*\t*,\nIDENT\tTheta\nIDENT\twrite\n(\t(\nIDENT\t5\n,\t,\nIDENT\t300\n)\t)\nIDENT\tread\n*\t*,\nIDENT\tl\nCOMMENT\t*\nCOMMENT\t*       Initialize other variables.\nCOMMENT\t*\nIDENT\tg\n=\t=\nIDENT\t9\n.\t.\nIDENT\t81\nIDENT\tThetaM\n=\t=\nIDENT\tTheta\n*\t*P\nIDENT\ti\n/\t/\nIDENT\t180\n.\t.\nIDENT\t0\nIDENT\tTheta\n=\t=\nIDENT\tThetaM\nIDENT\tt\n=\t=\nIDENT\t0\n.\t.\nIDENT\t0\nIDENT\tw\n=\t=\nIDENT\t0\n.\t.\nIDENT\t0\nIDENT\ta\n=\t=\n(\t(\n-\t-\nIDENT\tg\n/\t/\nIDENT\tl\n)\t)\n*\t*D\nIDENT\tSIN\n(\t(\nIDENT\tTheta\n)\t)\nCOMMENT\t*\nCOMMENT\t*       Loop until finished (angle.eq.-Theta_naught .or. omega = 0)?\nCOMMENT\t*\nIDENT\tCall\nIDENT\tEnterGraphicsMode\nIDENT\tdo\nIDENT\twhile\n(\t(\n.\t.\nIDENT\ttrue\n.\t.\n)\t)\nIDENT\ta\n=\t=\n(\t(\n-\t-\nIDENT\tg\n/\t/\nIDENT\tl\n)\t)\n*\t*D\nIDENT\tSIN\n(\t(\nIDENT\tTheta\n)\t)\nIDENT\tw\n=\t=\nIDENT\tw\n+\t+\nIDENT\ta\n*\t*d\nIDENT\tt\nIDENT\tTheta\n=\t=\nIDENT\tTheta\n+\t+\nIDENT\tw\n*\t*d\nIDENT\tt\nIDENT\tt\n=\t=\nIDENT\tt\n+\t+\nIDENT\tdt\nIDENT\tCall\nIDENT\tPlotBall\n(\t(\nIDENT\tTheta\n)\t)\nIDENT\tif\n(\t(\nIDENT\tTheta\n.\t.\nIDENT\tle\n.\t.\n(\t(\n-\t-\nIDENT\tThetaM\n)\t)\n)\t)\nIDENT\tgoto\nIDENT\t10\nIDENT\tenddo\nIDENT\t10\nIDENT\tcontinue\nCOMMENT\t*\nCOMMENT\t*       Print out final results.\nCOMMENT\t* \nIDENT\tprint\n*\t*,\nSTRING\t'Finished calculations.'\nIDENT\twrite\n(\t(\nIDENT\t5\n,\t,\nIDENT\t20\n)\t)\nIDENT\ta\n,\t,\nIDENT\tw\n,\t,\nIDENT\tTheta\n,\t,\nIDENT\tt\nCOMMENT\t*\nCOMMENT\t*       Program format statements.\nCOMMENT\t*\nIDENT\t20\nIDENT\tformat\n(\t(\nIDENT\t1\nIDENT\tx\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'Acceleration'\n,\t,\nIDENT\tT15\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'= '\n,\t,\nIDENT\tD12\n.\t.\nIDENT\t4\n/\t/\nIDENT\t1\nIDENT\t1\nIDENT\tx\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'Omega'\n,\t,\nIDENT\tT15\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'= '\n,\t,\nIDENT\tD12\n.\t.\nIDENT\t4\n/\t/\nIDENT\t2\nIDENT\t1\nIDENT\tx\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'Theta'\n,\t,\nIDENT\tT15\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'= '\n,\t,\nIDENT\tD12\n.\t.\nIDENT\t4\n/\t/\nIDENT\t3\nIDENT\t1\nIDENT\tx\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'Time'\n,\t,\nIDENT\tT15\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'= '\n,\t,\nIDENT\tD12\n.\t.\nIDENT\t4\n/\t/\n)\t)\nIDENT\t100\nIDENT\tformat\n(\t(\nIDENT\t1\nIDENT\tx\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'Enter real number for delta time in seconds: '\n,\t,\n)\t)\nIDENT\t200\nIDENT\tformat\n(\t(\nIDENT\t1\nIDENT\tx\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'Enter real number for Theta in degrees: '\n,\t,\n)\t)\nIDENT\t300\nIDENT\tformat\n(\t(\nIDENT\t1\nIDENT\tx\n,\t,\nSTRING\t'Enter real number for Length in meters: '\n,\t,\n)\t)\nIDENT\tCall\nIDENT\tExitGraphicsMode\nIDENT\tEnd\n"
